performs scheduling. Control cycle is divided
into realtime slot and configuration slot.
During realtime timeslot g is translated to JOG command
and the position and speed of defined group
of servos is read. During configuration slots herkulex_sced
and monotoring interface. It initialize servos
registers, provides operations to read and write
by high level component via corresponding method
